Cheetor:




Cheetor screeched, pinning his ears back. Something ringed. It wasn't just 
in his ears, it felt like it was in his head too. He hissed at Magmatron and 
bolted out of the near-by door. His tail flicked as he turned a corner. He 
had to get out of here, fast. He had to be in Predacon hands. He sprinted 
down the hallway, trying to find the exit-way of the base.
